the demise of social obligation, and the politics of neurological difference, Savarese argues for a reasonable commitment to human possibility and caring.', 'Reasonable People', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-17', '', '', '2010-09-06 12:27:23', '2010-09-06 19:27:23', '', 47, 'http://grantcuster.com/savarese/uncategorized/47-revision-17/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
