singly being taken up for its superior explanatory power.\r\n\r\nRead more of <a href="http://www.frontiersin.org/Integrative_Neuroscience/10.3389/fnint.2013.00006/full">Moving the Field: The Sensorimotor Perspective on Autism</a> as it appears in <a href="http://www.frontiersin.org/">frontiers</a>', 'Moving the Field: The Sensorimotor Perspective on Autism', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1066-revision-11', '', '', '2013-08-27 13:02:26', '2013-08-27 20:02:26', '', 1066, 'http://www.ralphsavarese.com/uncategorized/1066-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
